* 保存终极福利分析数据集
* ---------------------------------------------------------
display "💾 Saving the final advanced welfare dataset..."
save "D:\1-研究数据\EV充电\Panel_Welfare_Final_Advanced.dta", replace

display "🎉 Mission Accomplished! 全部图表已输出，结构性福利测算与偏差分析顺利完成！"

* =========================================================
* 附加模块：社会福利变动的结构性分解 (按电价时段 & 按时间)
* =========================================================
display "🧩 Decomposing Welfare Impact by Tariff Period and Time of Day..."

* ---------------------------------------------------------
* 1. 测算"尖、峰、平、谷"对单均福利变动的绝对贡献
* ---------------------------------------------------------
capture drop cs_jian cs_feng cs_ping cs_gu

* 使用 cond() 函数条件求和，完美拆解每个订单的总福利
bysort id: egen cs_jian = sum(cond(alt_status == "尖", Delta_CS, 0))
bysort id: egen cs_feng = sum(cond(alt_status == "峰", Delta_CS, 0))
bysort id: egen cs_ping = sum(cond(alt_status == "平", Delta_CS, 0))
bysort id: egen cs_gu   = sum(cond(alt_status == "谷", Delta_CS, 0))

preserve
* 去重，确保每个订单只展示一次
keep if choice == 1
display " "
display "======================================================================"
display "📊 结构性分解：尖、峰、平、谷 时段的单均期望福利变动贡献 (元/单)"
display "   (注：四者相加严格等于 total_Delta_CS。正值代表红利，负值代表剥夺)"
display "======================================================================"
* 打印 Mean(单均贡献) 和 Sum(样本总社会贡献)
tabstat cs_jian cs_feng cs_ping cs_gu total_Delta_CS, stat(mean sum) format(%15.3f) columns(variables)
